      "text": [
        " أَمَةٍ تَزْنِي قَالَ \"تُجْلَدُ نِصْفَ اَلْحَدِّ كَانَ لَهَا زَوْجٌ أَوْ لَمْ يَكُنْ لَهَا زَوْجٌ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5052 - Al-Hasan ibn Mahbub narrated from Al-Harith ibn Al-Ahwal from Burayd Al-ʿIjli from Abu Jafar Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) regarding a slave woman who commits adultery.\nImam (as) said: \"She is to be lashed half the prescribed punishment, whether she has a husband or does not have a husband.\""
        ]
      }
    },
